parameters:
Mage Relm: There's nothing here... Could it be that the
hunter lied!?

Mage Relm: This is troublesome... Huh? Nora-san, do you have
something to say to me?
Thief Nora: I'm right here~! Ah, Relm-san, behind you~!!
Mage Relm: Aaah!! W-Why are you behind me!?
Mage Relm: Haa haa... Ahh, that was a surprise...

Thief Nora: I'm glad you're safe! And with this, the request
is complete, right?!
Mage Relm: Yes, let's return to our adventure!
